{"tid":481070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位點睇25歲前結婚？","createTime":"2017-11-26T19:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T03:56:56.000Z","uid":138142,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3e79f0feddc831acb8abe5e78b3b9e167e9033c8","tid":481070,"uid":138142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:00:46.000Z","msg":"係咪會易啲離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n如果家境好少少會唔會好啲<br />\n<br />\n岩岩上ig見到youtube嗰個jade條仔同佢求佐婚有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/030020_cc53156208f139dc48eeeb79bf211246.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F030020_cc53156208f139dc48eeeb79bf211246.jpg&h=937572db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/030022_3b410d9e77828466816d869f2c27ee59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F030022_3b410d9e77828466816d869f2c27ee59.jpg&h=f8bab7ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條女好似係96年"},{"pid":"cdd7aece5bfaffafa3a04a316457f21b12cd9441","tid":481070,"uid":138142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:05:29.000Z","msg":"有冇巴或絲25歲前就結佐婚？"},{"pid":"21cd5b580fd4445d82786f8be5896e00753a62ac","tid":481070,"uid":124941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:06:03.000Z","msg":"我都想"},{"pid":"662fe23925c96c639d3974112c3766651486ee79","tid":481070,"uid":118211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:07:16.000Z","msg":"想早婚...但今世唔得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f3952ff2ff98f8716a6bb1573079178ca74e49","tid":481070,"uid":138142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想</blockquote><br />\n但係好多人話會好易離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8653906769e01b5d1ed4304d2ff1b437e59a70","tid":481070,"uid":138142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想早婚...但今世唔得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲婚有遲婚好 可以玩到30幾歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5f62b0fdf69bcd95e74438237a15380b0070e1","tid":481070,"uid":815,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:13:21.000Z","msg":"有錢就無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n眼見識得有啲人兩公婆住公屋學歷又低<br />\n25歲未夠就結婚 仲生埋細路<br />\n我心諗佢地生個細路出嚟都係受苦受難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6d651adbdb93d2225c83ce84d188ff6740dedc","tid":481070,"uid":151774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:19:15.000Z","msg":"通常都係靚女嫁先<br />\n街市買嘢都係好嘢俾人清哂<br />\n無話好唔好 睇個人價值同埋男仔嘅消費能力"},{"pid":"e206a96db2e120596baaac277bca4de64db01bc3","tid":481070,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:19:52.000Z","msg":"識人19歲定20就結"},{"pid":"5c3535a3f531569ae0cead822171b9eb52962d38","tid":481070,"uid":90706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:25:25.000Z","msg":"25歲結到婚，除佐唔小心搞大個肚呢批之外 <br />\n其他多數喺屋企本身有一定積蓄，兩者或其中一個已經有一定事業基礎 <br />\n但話分兩頭，有幾多個25歲真喺識思考人生？完全成熟應付各種家庭問題？ 腦筍是否完整？ <br />\n煮飯都未必熟手，點玩？ 貪新鮮？ <br />\n冇事業基礎，靠愛殺出一條血路真喺拿兩個人幸福較飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過首先你要有......... <br />\n然而我冇 亦唔想25歲前結婚."},{"pid":"c55c41eaa817cd7fd71eed37aecff1d879e66181","tid":481070,"uid":36478,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪會易啲離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n如果家境好少少會唔會好啲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">岩岩上ig見到youtube嗰個jade條仔</span>同佢求<span style=\"color: red;\">佐</span>婚有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/030020_cc53156208f139dc48eeeb79bf211246.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F030020_cc53156208f139dc48eeeb79bf211246.jpg&h=937572db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/030022_3b410d9e77828466816d869f2c27ee59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F030022_3b410d9e77828466816d869f2c27ee59.jpg&h=f8bab7ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條女好似係96年</blockquote><br />\n唔撚識<br />\n佐你老母"},{"pid":"3b594298524950338ff902a32de751f864120b5e","tid":481070,"uid":138142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:38:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢就無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n眼見識得有啲人兩公婆住公屋學歷又低<br />\n25歲未夠就結婚 仲生埋細路<br />\n我心諗佢地生個細路出嚟都係受苦受難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又係仲要住喺間細屋日日睇住老豆老母嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b751da1867aeceeac32d44f443392190a253a2c2","tid":481070,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老婆23同我結左，冇大肚<br />\n係美國做野，叫做有車有樓<br />\n兩老係香港唔洗我養<br />\n<br />\n算係咁啦...佢都仲讀緊master<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生活剛剛夠唔洗捱窮"},{"pid":"f5c2482c2141e5cbd1eba65d7490b61b98b11c8c","tid":481070,"uid":138142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老婆23同我結左，冇大肚<br />\n係美國做野，叫做有車有樓<br />\n兩老係香港唔洗我養<br />\n<br />\n算係咁啦...佢都仲讀緊master<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生活剛剛夠唔洗捱窮</blockquote><br />\n勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家結佐婚幾多年？ 介唔介意講你做貴行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004ccac2b288e611345675d2c7034d0f65443e08","tid":481070,"uid":138142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:41:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識人19歲定20就結</blockquote><br />\n感情好唔好嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798ad0892d3ecbd3013c5f4d22f2ffa1669c52b3","tid":481070,"uid":127272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:42:28.000Z","msg":"咁後生就想戴綠帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e103d3b250dfff12751d338aacfe25ad5a86e1d","tid":481070,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:42:35.000Z","msg":"同居仲好啦"},{"pid":"c7f1d8f32da96fdf03bc41e845bf9dc1f83637c7","tid":481070,"uid":138142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:42:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>25歲結到婚，除佐唔小心搞大個肚呢批之外 <br />\n其他多數喺屋企本身有一定積蓄，兩者或其中一個已經有一定事業基礎 <br />\n但話分兩頭，有幾多個25歲真喺識思考人生？完全成熟應付各種家庭問題？ 腦筍是否完整？ <br />\n煮飯都未必熟手，點玩？ 貪新鮮？ <br />\n冇事業基礎，靠愛殺出一條血路真喺拿兩個人幸福較飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過首先你要有......... <br />\n然而我冇 亦唔想25歲前結婚.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有家底嗰堆可能請埋工人 不過同時都好大誘惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79b02eec558941b408c80bf8f96651ffb8a496a","tid":481070,"uid":138142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁後生就想戴綠帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個心未定"},{"pid":"d7c49b9a19b0c89ac474685084c4b21a2ea97ce7","tid":481070,"uid":90706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>25歲結到婚，除佐唔小心搞大個肚呢批之外 <br />\n其他多數喺屋企本身有一定積蓄，兩者或其中一個已經有一定事業基礎 <br />\n但話分兩頭，有幾多個25歲真喺識思考人生？完全成熟應付各種家庭問題？ 腦筍是否完整？ <br />\n煮飯都未必熟手，點玩？ 貪新鮮？ <br />\n冇事業基礎，靠愛殺出一條血路真喺拿兩個人幸福較飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過首先你要有......... <br />\n然而我冇 亦唔想25歲前結婚.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有家底嗰堆可能請埋工人 不過同時都好大誘惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有家底 有能力請工人， 只要妳唔討厭對方，對方又肯娶/嫁，一般人可能真喺已經狗衝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n話知佢未來喺點"},{"pid":"215fffcf78de9c697a5c3f93f4a51317985bb994","tid":481070,"uid":4709,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T20:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老婆23同我結左，冇大肚<br />\n係美國做野，叫做有車有樓<br />\n兩老係香港唔洗我養<br />\n<br />\n算係咁啦...佢都仲讀緊master<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生活剛剛夠唔洗捱窮</blockquote><br />\n勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家結佐婚幾多年？ 介唔介意講你做貴行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係好耐...佢今年24<br />\n我就做室內設計，未計bonus花紅有35k hkd<br />\n我老婆都就黎畢業，做營養師，佢出到黎應該高人工過我<br />\n<br />\n晚晚我煮飯佢洗碗，一齊打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好開心"},{"pid":"1ad546b10b727e5c3a484f752e7bb58def86b262","tid":481070,"uid":146924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T21:21:02.000Z","msg":"大家覺得男同女理想結婚嘅年齡係幾多歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">話時話外國啲人唔知點解好多大學就結</span>"},{"pid":"7c62e7173191abff0619b29cce02c0ab3774496a","tid":481070,"uid":106149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T21:23:25.000Z","msg":"96年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我以為28....29歲"},{"pid":"331b0b3b41ec4087924c4b99408ab2868386a83d","tid":481070,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:58:32.000Z","msg":"父幹"},{"pid":"8312e48f139c5d404f38f3a02bb4f20e17d651ab","tid":481070,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"老實，早少少生同個細路思想脫節冇咁快"}]}